{
  "transcript_id": "10162.6",
  "source_file": "10162.6.json",
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "chunk_words_setting": 800,
  "n_chunks": 2,
  "sentences": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is my husband, Alan Friedberg.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's OK.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, during all of these interviews and conversations with Aniko, I keep thinking about-- I had family in Europe also.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father had a brother and a sister who had family.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never knew any of them.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And these were my cousins.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- they all-- one day, we knew that they had disappeared.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so this is to me kind of striking also.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it-- of course it hits home with Aniko.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it-- it hits home also, it gets me back to many years ago in the late 1930s when I was aware that these things started to go on.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in Latvia, right?",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Latvia.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hm.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thank you for coming.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is my parents' wedding photo taken in Budapest, I guess, in 1927.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And your mother's full name?",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ilona Benedek.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father Ferenc, at that time, Ferenc Weisz.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Tell us about this?",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This happens to be the only picture I have from my young age.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I must be five or six years old here in some kind of ballet performance.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Debrecen-- in Debrecen.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hungary.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is the only picture I have left with my mother and father.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents",
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess this must have been taken around 1933 or so in Debrecen.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is-- this is that photo I mentioned earlier about my mother.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father-- we had this taken together to send it to my father just a few months before we were taken away.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the right shoulder you see that pale spot?",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's where my head was.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my father had it removed and enlarged.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Health",
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had it always next to his bed.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Health",
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is my uncle, Tibor Benedek, in Paris, who is photographed with a friend of his-- Miss [INAUDIBLE].",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She used to be very famous at one time-- a friend of Chevalier's, a singer, dancer.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's why I went to Paris.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother knew also Miss [INAUDIBLE].",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she used to go to Paris and visit and stay at her house by Versailles.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is my father in a coal mine when his invention was introduced.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor",
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is under Stalinism in Hungary.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's called a hydraulically marching mine machine.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's-- it's still-- it's still used in Hungarian as well as all Russian coal mines.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I must have been maybe '54, '55.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mentioned earlier that Revlon-- actually Charles Revson, who was the owner of Revlon-- hired me to head-- to be the expert of-- the fragrance expert of Revlon.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were just going into the perfume business in New York.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is why I stayed in America.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was my first job.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is-- they had a publicity picture made of me.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is just a proof, an unretouched proof that they have given me.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is in 1961.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In New York.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is my daughter, Anne.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was a year ago this summer, past summer.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was right here in the back of-- behind the house.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was visiting here in Huntington, yes.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She lives in Fort Lauderdale.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is my darling only grandson, Alexandre.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this picture was taken about three weeks ago.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was just visiting and gave it to me.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He is eight years old.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he is the son of my darling son, who even though I cannot find a current picture of him, he is nothing to be ashamed of.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He is a very good-looking and wonderful guy.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So since that reunion in Germany I was telling you about, they erected a museum in this-- on the site of the old [?",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dynamit ?] [?",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobel ?] headquarters, which was a landmark building.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it really is a quite remarkable building.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was invited for the opening.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was also commissioned to make the only sculpture there.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this is the catalog from that museum, which is called also a documentation and informational center.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this is the catalog with-- with a photo of my sculpture on the cover, which represents slave laborers there, the way they were-- like the two figures are like one.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One is-- one is with a bowed head, humiliated, heavy in-- heavily-- heavy labor carrying the grenade.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the other one is-- is standing-- standing erect looking upward and letting a bird fly off, representing freedom and our hope.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was in '93-- '93 or '94 even.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's when I-- I recall-- the sculpture was commissioned.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was a landmark building.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It took a long time to-- to build it just so.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the-- it wasn't inaugurated until '94.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, my professional name is Aniko Veres-Fe, which Aniko Veres is my maiden name and Fe was added because of other things.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is the January 16, 1995 edition of magazine, which was an Auschwitz memorial edition that I happened open by chance.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I found myself in this picture, which represents us, part of the 1,000 Hungarian girls, on our way from Auschwitz to this German factory.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I happen to be the tall girl right on the crease.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is a homemade photograph of the-- of a maquette-- of the only holocaust memorial that I ever designed.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Post-conflict"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I always believe just like I don't think that-- that words can convey-- convey the inexplicable, the-- the-- the human tragedy that was the Holocaust, I feel the same way about the ability of visual arts to do that.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this I see as preferably a larger than life size bronze-- what--",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--would call it?",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's thin slab, like a--",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--slab, where the figures, the figure of a family, would be cut out.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it's of the void, the void that it represents in the lives, in the hearts of the survivors as well.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is a side view, obviously.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the other part of the sculpture is that it would have to be on a large bare terrain.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the way the sun moves or reflectors, it always casts a shadow where the figures emerge in light.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I feel simplicity is the strongest.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's the only thing that I would hope to one day to execute.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    }
  ]
}